[SN]TITLE[SN]
Ebbw Vale appoint Lee Davies as head coach following Nigel Davies departure

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Ebbw Vale have confirmed forwards coach Lee Davies as head coach following the departure of Nigel Davies.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Former Wales and Scarlets head coach Davies stepped down from his role after two years in charge of the Welsh Premiership side.
"I am extremely honoured to be given the opportunity to become head coach of such a prestigious club," Lee Davies said.
The Steelmen have also confirmed Ben Daniels as attack and backs coach.
